          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Article 4 -->
        <article class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden animate-on-scroll hover:shadow-xl transition-all hidden" data-article="4">
          <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/590041/pexels-photo-590041.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" 
               alt="Marketing Analytics" 
               class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
          />
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
              <span class="bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mr-3">Analytics</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm">7 min read</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Marketing Attribution: Track What Actually Drives Revenue</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Stop guessing which marketing channels work. Learn how to set up proper attribution tracking and measure true marketing ROI.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3184317/pexels-photo-3184317.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=40&h=40&fit=crop" 
                     alt="Alex Johnson" 
                     class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full mr-2 object-cover"
                />
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Alex Johnson</span>
              </div>
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Jan 8, 2024</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Article 5 -->
        <article class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden animate-on-scroll hover:shadow-xl transition-all hidden" data-article="5">
          <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/196644/pexels-photo-196644.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" 
               alt="Landing Page Optimization" 
               class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
          />
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
              <span class="bg-secondary-100 text-secondary-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mr-3">CRO</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm">9 min read</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Landing Page Optimization: 15 Elements That Boost Conversions</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Transform your landing pages into conversion machines with these 15 proven optimization techniques that increased our clients' conversion rates by 40%.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3184291/pexels-photo-3184291.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=40&h=40&fit=crop" 
                     alt="Lisa Thompson" 
                     class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full mr-2 object-cover"
                />
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Lisa Thompson</span>
              </div>
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Jan 5, 2024</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Article 6 -->
        <article class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden animate-on-scroll hover:shadow-xl transition-all hidden" data-article="6">
          <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3184306/pexels-photo-3184306.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" 
               alt="Marketing Strategy" 
               class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
          />
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
              <span class="bg-accent-100 text-accent-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mr-3">Strategy</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm">10 min read</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Building a Marketing Strategy That Scales with Your Business</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Learn how to create a marketing strategy that grows with your business, from startup to enterprise, with frameworks used by our most successful clients.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3184338/pexels-photo-3184338.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=40&h=40&fit=crop" 
                     alt="Sarah Chen" 
                     class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full mr-2 object-cover"
                />
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Sarah Chen</span>
              </div>
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Jan 3, 2024</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-12 animate-on-scroll">
        <button id="load-more-btn" class="bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
          Load More Articles
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Free Resources -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-on-scroll">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Free Marketing Resources</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">Download our proven templates, checklists, and guides</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Resource 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 animate-on-scroll hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
            </svg>
